# Desktoper
A simple QT6/C++ utility for launching applications on specific X11 workspaces (virtual desktops) using `wmctrl`

## Features
Launch applications on any workspace (virtual desktop: gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences num-workspaces)

### Prerequisites
- Debian 12/Ubuntu 22.04
- `wmctrl` command-line utility

#### Install Dependencies
sudo apt update
sudo apt install wmctrl
